{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SetupAutomation"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"SetupAutomation","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" provides version-specific keyboard input sequences","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that walk through the macOS Setup Assistant without any human","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"interaction. After the sequence completes, the VM has:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A user account (configurable, defaults to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"admin"},{"text":"\/","type":"text"},{"code":"admin","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":")","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"SSH (Remote Login) enabled"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A UTC timezone configured","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Design","level":2,"anchor":"Design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This follows the approach pioneered by","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/cirruslabs\/tart","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" for Packer","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"boot_command"},{"type":"text","text":" automation. The sequences have been verified against"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Tart’s working Packer plugin and adapted for direct use via the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Virtualization framework’s keyboard API."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Requirements","level":2,"anchor":"Requirements"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content"